.SH Description
\f[CR]SHCrossPowerSpectrumDensityC\f[R] will calculate the cross\-power
spectral density of two complex functions expressed in complex 4\-pi
normalized spherical harmonics.
For a given spherical harmonic degree \f[CR]l\f[R], this is calculated
as:
